Ukraine Oil Producer Ukrnafta Picks Scherban as Finance Director

-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 
2011-06-06T16:11:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/ukraine-oil-producer-ukrnafta-picks-scherban-as-finance-director.html
VAT Ukrnafta, a Ukrainian state-
controlled oil producer, said it appointed Artem Scherban as
finance director, while Michael Bakunenko, a former Goldman
Sachs employee, will be director of corporate development and
strategy.  The Kiev-based company also hired Alan Sutton as head of
economy and planning, and David Sturt to manage the upstream
business, with a focus on stabilizing production levels and
stimulating exploration, Ukrnafta said today in an e-mailed
statement.  “We expect to announce a number of strategic initiatives
in the near future,” Chief Executive Officer Peter Vanhecke
said in the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
